[PER Seigel] stated -- 
The [MISC Israeli] government has never asked the [ORG NSG] for any exemption to nuclear supply guidelines or made any [MISC Israeli-specific] request of the [ORG NSG] . 
[LOC Israel] is recognized as a full-fledged adherent to the [MISC NSG Guidelines] . 
