[LOC Russian Federation] ( RU ) 
International ; science ; energy ; weapons 
A high-security [MISC Russian] laboratory complex storing anthrax , plague and other deadly bacteria faces loosing electricity for lack of payment to the mosenergo electric utility . 
A large repository of anthrax , plague and other deadly bacteria stored in a high-security [MISC Russian] laboratory complex 100 miles south of [LOC Moscow] is facing the threat of loosing electricity . 
An official from the [LOC Moscow] region 's mosenergo electric utility arrived recently at the [MISC Russian] laboratory complex and threatened to turn off the electricity for lack of payment . 
The [MISC Russian] laboratory complex is a 90-building campus and served as the location for [LOC Russia] 's secret biological weapons program in the [LOC Soviet] era . 
An incorrect headline in the newspaper [ORG Izvestia] stated that deadly viruses from a [LOC Moscow] regional depository threaten [LOC Moscow] . 
There are no viruses at the [ORG State Scientific Center of applied Microbiology] in obolensk . 
At the [ORG State Scientific Center of applied] microbiology there is every kind of deadly bacteria that was studied for use in the secret biological weapons program of the [LOC Soviet Union] . 
A large virus repository is located in [LOC Siberia] . 
Both [MISC Russian] and [MISC Western] officials have stated that it is unlikely that any public health threat would result from a power cutoff at the [ORG State Scientific Center of] applied microbiology . 
[MISC Russian] and [MISC Western] officials have stated that there is enough uncertainty that they could not be positive a loss of power at the [ORG State Scientific Center of applied] microbiology would not cause a public health threat . 
