The [LOC United States] dissuaded [PER Cardoso] from signing the decree out of concern that the accidental downing of civilian aircraft could expose the [LOC US] government and companies to lawsuits . 
20010400 the [LOC United States] reduced previous support for operations targeting drug-running aircraft when a [MISC Peruvian] jet shot down a small plane misidentified as a drug carrier and killed an [MISC American] missionary and her child . 
