Neither the hacking claim nor an [MISC Iranian] assertion that group [ORG XP] was based in the [LOC United Arab Emirates] could be verified independently . 
Several [MISC Iranian] news sites stated on 19 September 2008 that many of the [MISC Shiite] and [MISC Iran-related] web sites that had been attacked were running normally again . 
