Reports claim that all of the 1000 [MISC Muslim] men with military training are over the age of 18 . 
Muslims Against Illegitimate Leaders is a [LOC Cape Town-based] group . 
The report was refuted by the [ORG Muslim Judicial Council] . 
[LOC South Africa] 's [ORG Foreign Ministry] stated that [LOC South Africa] 's [ORG Foreign Military Assistance Act] prohibits the recruitment of people inside or outside of [LOC South Africa] for mercenary or foreign military assistance . 
[LOC South Africa] 's [ORG Foreign Military Assistance Act] means that no person is allowed to offer military assistance to any State , organ of State , group or other country , unless permission is granted by the [ORG National Conventional Arms Control Committee] . 
[LOC South Africa] 's [ORG Foreign Military Assistance Act] means that foreign military assistance could be rendered only in accordance with an agreement approved by the [ORG National Conventional Arms Control Committee] . 
The [MISC South African] [ORG Foreign Ministry] stated that any person found in violation of [LOC South Africa] 's [ORG Foreign Military Assistance Act] or any person that fails to receive permission to participate in foreign military activities could be prosecuted and sentenced to a fine , imprisonment or both . 
