On 020724 the police dispatched over 100 staff reportedly stormed a propitiation dance and wine party organized to settle some disputes by 2 triad groups at a disco nightclub in mongkok , [LOC Kowloon] . 
The police eventually arrested 3 branch leaders and 14 core Triad members . 
