[LOC Hong Kong] police sources were quoted as saying that the success of the operation in netting all 17 was the result of the police 's effort to infiltrate into the relevant gangs here . 
Police sources also intimated that more crackdowns by the [LOC Hong Kong] Police on other [ORG Triad] gangs will follow . 
The [LOC Hong Kong] police 's effort in fighting organized criminals involves actively cooperating with police on the [MISC Chinese] mainland and in other regions . 
The first so-called targeting [MISC Conference of the] [ORG International Drug Enforcement Conference] ( [ORG IDEC] ) far east region was held in [LOC Hong Kong] earlier in 020700 . 
[LOC Hong Kong] was chosen to host the event following the decision of the [ORG IDEC] meeting held in [LOC Bolivia] in 020200 . 
Some 42 senior anti-narcotics officers from the [MISC Chinese] mainland , [LOC Hong Kong] , [LOC Australia] , [LOC Indonesia] , [LOC Japan] , [LOC South Korea] , [LOC Myanmar] , the [LOC Philippines] , [LOC Singapore] , [LOC Thailand] and the [LOC United States] met . 
The [LOC Hong Kong] police 's internal news letter recently reported that the conference aimed to provide a flexible and forward-thinking environment for sharing information and taking positive action against the organized criminals of transnational drug trafficking . 
The [LOC Hong Kong] police 's exchange of intelligence with the police on the [MISC Chinese] mainland has been particularly intense . 
An 11-member delegation from mainland [LOC China] 's [ORG National Narcotics Control Commission] visited [LOC Hong Kong] recently to study how the police here enforce their anti-narcotics laws . 
The 11-person team was chaired by the Deputy Director of [ORG Bureau of] narcotics control of the [ORG Chinese Ministry of Public Security Chen] cunyi and was briefed by the [LOC Hong Kong] Police as led by [LOC Hong Kong] 's head of narcotics bureau [PER Ip Lau Chuen] on enforced actions carried out in [LOC Hong Kong] . 
The [LOC Hong Kong] police and [LOC China] 's [ORG National Narcotics Control Commission] also exchanged mutual concerns and discussed a number of issues which included investigations to counter drug trafficking and money laundering activities . 
The mainland party closed their visit after meeting with [LOC Hong Kong] 's deputy assistant commissioner for crime [PER Yam] [MISC TAT] wing and held discussions on a proposal to further cooperate in combating cross-boundary drug trafficking activities . 
