The communique said [LOC China] and [LOC Kyrgyzstan] are also ready to expand cooperation in economy and other fields with other [ORG SCO] members , promote the relations between the [ORG SCO] and other countries and international organizations , and strengthen the [ORG SCO] 's role in maintaining regional and global peace and development . 
