Premier [PER Peng Li] and [MISC Kirghizian] President [PER Akayev] attended the signing ceremony . 
The six documents are : an agreement on [MISC Chinese] providing a loan to the [LOC Kirghizia] government , an agreement on forming a combined [LOC Economy] and [ORG Trade Committee] between the Sino - [ORG Kirghizian] governments , an note exchange on the presenting of materials to [LOC Kirghizia] by [LOC China] , a cultural cooperation agreement between the two countries of [LOC China] and [LOC Kirghizia] , ratification letters on exchanging consular treaties between the two countries , an agreement on cooperating on the [ORG China Trade Promotion Council] and the [ORG Kirghizian Chamber of Industry and Commerce] . 
