[PER Akayev] highly commended the results of the conference with [PER Peng Li] 
He expressed that , this visit by Premier [PER Peng Li] would promote the peace , security and stability of the [MISC Central Asian] region . 
He felt that , the recently signed documents were very important in enforcing good neighborhood relations and friendly cooperation between both countries . 
