He expressed hopes that the [LOC Central] [MISC Asian] region would be stable and developed , and that the standard of living of the people would continuously improve . 
[PER Peng Li] hoped that the [ORG Kirghizian] news media would relay greetings from the [MISC Chinese] people to the [ORG Kirghizian] people . 
