[ORG Xinhua News Agency] , [LOC Tokyo] , September 1st , by reporter [PER Yiguo Yu] 
The [MISC Japanese] delegation participating in the [MISC Sixth Far East] and [ORG South Pacific Region Handicapped Sports Meet] held a grand swearing in ceremony in [LOC Tokyo] this afternoon . 
A [MISC Japanese] flag hung from the Chairman 's stage . 
Sportsmen , coaches , doctors , nurses and officials of the delegation sat neatly below the stage . 
An atmosphere of confidence and eagerness for progress filled the ceremony ground . 
Vice-minister of the [MISC Japanese] State [ORG Welfare Ministry] , [PER Souyasen] , delivered a " bolstering departure speech " to the delegation . 
[PER Souya] said , the [ORG Far South Sports Meet] was an international sports meet that attracts the world 's attention , and the scale of this sports meet to be held in [LOC Beijing] is the largest to date . 
He hoped that all the athletes would " fully demonstrate the strength and skill that they cultivate daily , as the competitors representing [LOC Japan] , they should carry out competition with athletes from various countries honestly " . 
[ORG Souya] emphasized , the [MISC Japanese] delegation must make use of this opportunity of participation in the [LOC Beijing] Far South Sports Meet " to deepen friendship with athletes from various countries , and expand the scope of international friendliness . " 
[ORG Souya] handed over the delegation flag of the [MISC Japanese] delegation to the head of the delegation and Director of the [LOC Tokyo] Handicapped [ORG Integrated Sports Center] , [ORG Banminyan] . 
From this tight , orderly , warm and serious swearing in ceremony , this reporter felt that , the [MISC Japanese] Handicapped Sports Team was a team that was well trained , disciplined and possessed fighting spirit . 
The [MISC Japanese] delegation will fly to [LOC Beijing] on the 2nd . 
After the closing ceremonies of the Sports Meet , they will continue to remain in [LOC Beijing] for two days , to carry out interaction activities with relevant [MISC Chinese] parties and visit and tour , and return to [LOC Japan] on 13th . 
