[ORG Xinhua News Agency] , [LOC Seoul] , August 31st , by reporter [PER Shuifu Tang] 
The first " [PER Le] [MISC Tian Cup] " [LOC China] and [LOC Korea] Go competition started today at [LOC Fushan] , the second largest city of [LOC Korea] . 
In the first round of competition , the [MISC Chinese] team defeated the relatively stronger [MISC Korean] team with a score of 4 : 3 . 
In the competition today , both sides each have 7 Go players participating . 
Weiping Nie ( 9th level ) , [PER Xiaoguang Liu] ( 9th level ) , [PER Hao Chang] ( 6th level ) and [PER Dayuan Cao] ( 9th level ) from the [MISC Chinese] team defeated [PER Guibing Cui] ( 6th level ) , [PER Xiuying Zhang] ( 9th level ) , [PER Fengzhu Xu] ( 9th level ) and [PER Xuange Lin] ( 8th level ) from the [MISC Korean] team respectively . 
Among which , [PER Weiping Nie] , [PER Xiaoguang Liu] and [PER Hao Chang] both achieved victories in the middle games . 
[PER Dayuan Cao] achieved victory with an advantage of seven and a half ' mu ' . 
[PER Xunxuan Cao] ( 9th level ) , [PER Changhao Li] ( 7th level ) and [PER Changhe Liu] ( 6th level ) from the [MISC Korean] team defeated [PER Jing Liu] ( 5th level ) , [PER Xiaocun Ma] ( 9th level ) and [PER Jianhong Wang] ( 7th level ) from the [MISC Chinese] team respectively . 
Among which , [PER Xunxuan Cao] achieved a victory in the middle game . 
[PER Changhao Li] and [PER Changhe Liu] achieved victories with advantages of six and a half ' mu ' and seven and a half ' mu ' respectively . 
When receiving reporters telephone interviews , [PER Runan Wang] , leader of the [MISC Chinese] delegation presented that , overall speaking , the strength of the [MISC Korean] team was stronger than the [MISC Chinese] team . 
However , the [MISC Chinese] team performed better today , and therefore achieved victory . 
The performance of our young competitor , [PER Hao Chang] , was especially outstanding today , defeating [PER Fengzhu Xu] of the [MISC Korean] team in the middle game . 
[PER Fengzhu Xu] has won many championships in international competitions before . 
He had achieved complete victory in nine games with [MISC Chinese] Go players before . 
The Go teams from [LOC China] and [LOC Korea] will shift to [LOC Seoul] on September 1st , and will hold the second competition in the [LOC Le Tian Hotel] on the 2nd . 
According to the rules discussed and agreed upon by both sides , if the two teams draw with 7 : 7 , then the final result will be determined by the result of the competition between [PER Weiping Nie] of the [MISC Chinese] team and [PER Xunxuan Cao] of the [MISC Korean] team . 
The prize money of the competition this time is 100,000 [LOC US] dollars , the team that wins will get 70,000 [LOC US] dollars , while the team that loses will get 30,000 [LOC US] dollars . 
( End ) 
[ORG Xinhua News Agency] , [LOC Rome] , September 1st , by reporters [PER Aiguo Yang] and [PER Changrui Huang] 
The 1 - meter diving board preliminaries of the [MISC Seventh World Swimming Championship] were held here this morning . 
[MISC Chinese] competitor [PER Lan Wei] and [PER Sheng Chen] both received qualification for the semi-finals . 
In the preliminaries , [PER Wei Lan] , who is 26 years old this year , from [LOC Guangdong] , with outstanding skill , occupied the lead position with a total score of 355.35 points . 
[PER Sheng Chen] , who is 19 years old this year , from [LOC Hubei] , is temporarily in the sixth position , the a total score of 342.60 points . 
The competitor who is temporarily in second place is the [MISC German] athlete [PER Bao Lizuo] , with a total score of 355.02 points , slightly lower than [PER Wei Lan] . 
The competitor from [LOC Zimbabwe] , [PER Si Aiwan] , who is temporarily in third place , has a total score of 354.39 points . 
After the competition , the chief coach of the [MISC Chinese] diving team said to our agency 's reporter : " [PER Sheng Chen] is a little nervous today . " 
He also said : " Our athletes are not very used to carrying out competition under strong sunlight . " 
At home , they carry out indoor training mostly . 
Looks like we still need to train more outdoors . " 
He felt that , there were more new competitors from our country participating in this competition . 
They still lack experience in international competitions . 
The preliminary competition for the women 's 10 - meter platform diving will be held this afternoon . 
[PER Mingxia Fu] , who won the championship for our country at the [MISC World Championship] and the [MISC Olympic Games] , and the competitor from [LOC Hebei] , [PER Bin Chi] , who won the championship at the [MISC World Cup] will participate in the competition . 
( End ) 
